actions.text: Referred to the House Committee on Natural Resources.

official_title: Providing for congressional disapproval under chapter 8 of title 5, United States Code, of the rule submitted by the United States Fish and Wildlife Service relating to "Migratory Bird Hunting; 2024-25 Seasons for Certain Migratory Game Birds".
